{"tid":842033,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 李嘉欣依靠老公肩膀享受二人世界","createTime":"2018-09-30T03:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T08:08:17.000Z","uid":48905,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae0b9fbebc47c2cf52eab511608addb2cdcce58","tid":842033,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T03:45:47.000Z","msg":"48歲的李嘉欣自從結婚生子後，雖然遠離了影視圈，但時不時的撒一下狗糧，讓人感受她幸福的模樣。9月29日晚，李嘉欣通過微博曬和老公許晉亨的恩愛合影，並稱：「好似人地王晶咁癡心情長劍咁，可以樣樣野都為晒邱淑貞去做，咁樣做對於你來講係侮辱你既智慧係戇居丫嘛！咁你咪要去抬起其他人囉，鍾意去同埋其他女人上床囉！打工仔？打工仔你使對人咁好個呵？你對邊個好？你對Ada唔好咩？成街人都睇死你開公司，仲開戲畀佢拍呀！咁多聯絡架？唔洗講野啦我地。我真係恭喜你呀，簽左個洪欣咁蠢既西．．．西女人返去！恭喜你快撚Ｄ捧紅佢添呀！你無諗住捧佢簽佢來把撚呀？」<br />\n<br />\n照片中，李嘉欣和老公坐在水池邊，一副小鳥依人的倚靠在老公肩膀上，十分的恩愛幸福。李嘉欣還戴上眼鏡，更顯知性美，一身運動打扮又活力十足。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/114348_043fb384ad3c9aee03f47c98ff40d2a1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F114348_043fb384ad3c9aee03f47c98ff40d2a1.png&h=39d3e29f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/114350_9e0187f716df2525015bac10510e57d8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F114350_9e0187f716df2525015bac10510e57d8.png&h=f207ce4a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8687ea98e1df7023b8e39441e14e8464bb9f042d","tid":842033,"uid":136502,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T03:56:26.000Z","msg":"48睇落仲似28<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aeb87a9f62b08ccfa0c4ae01f06f2668eb910e8","tid":842033,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T04:24:46.000Z","msg":"把撚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.